    "At present, there is a general lack of relevant regulations for AI regulation in the financial sector.",
    "Historical experience shows that if financial innovation is excessively ahead of regulation, it will not only lead to financial risks, but also threaten financial stability.",
    "It could also trigger an excessive regulatory backlash and stifle the development of beneficial financial innovation.",
    "Therefore, based on the principle of \"same risk, same supervision\", the financial management sector can carefully consider the risks and challenges that AI may bring to the financial sector.Finally, international cooperation on AI regulation should be strengthened.",
    "International competition and cooperation in AI regulation are taking place."
